sense.def:
To oscillate
pomeni ponavljajoče se premikati iz ene lege v drugo in nazaj.

seg.quote: Its wings oscillate up and down.

sense.def:
To oscillate between two moods, attitudes, or types of behaviour
pomeni nenehno prehajati iz enega razpoloženja v drugega in nazaj.

seg.quote: His mood oscillated between co-operation and aggression.
